1.title: Support for the State of Israel
1.description: Expresses support for the State of Israel.

2.title: Human Trafficking/Abduction of Nigerian Girls
2.description: Condemns abduction of Nigerian girls by the Boko Haram terrorist group, calls for the girls' release, & urges increased worldwide efforts to combat human trafficking, particularly of women and girls.

3.title: Establishing the Congressional Districts of the State
3.description: Revising the state's congressional districts; providing for the inclusion of unlisted territory in contiguous districts; providing for the inclusion of noncontiguous territory; providing that new counties become part of the congressional district in which the territory for such new county is located; providing for the election of representatives to the United States House of Representatives; providing that an appointment made pursuant to former district boundaries is unaffected by new district boundaries, etc.
